						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up in the street opposite the village headman's house.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1389, Sarvadhāri, Mārgaśira.</hi> However, the weekday is lost in which case the details of the date may be equivalent to 1468 A.D., November.</p>						

						<p>Damaged. It records a gift of some grain income by <hi rend="italic">mahāmaṇḍalēśvara</hi> Golla-Prōli Jaggarājadēva Mahārāju for the maintenance of the tank of the village Chilamanūru.</p>						

						</summary>
